t}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category|Liam Henderson}}\n*{{Soccerbase}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Henderson, Liam}}\n[[Category:1989 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Gateshead]]\n[[Category:English footballers]]\n[[Category:Association football forwards]]\n[[Category:Hartlepool United F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Watford F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Wealdstone F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Colchester United F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Aldershot Town F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Rotherham United F.C. players]]\n[[Category:York City F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Forest Green Rovers F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Gainsborough Trinity F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Gateshead F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Spennymoor Town F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Morpeth Town A.F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Isthmian League players]]\n[[Category:English Football League players]]\n[[Category:National League (English football) players]]\n", "text_old": "{{Use British English|date=August 2013}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=November 2012}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name                = Liam Henderson\n| image               = Liam Henderson.jpg\n| image_size          = 200\n| caption             = Henderson in 2010\n| fullname            = Liam Marc Henderson<ref name=\"Hugman2010-11\">{{cite book\n | editor-first = Barry J.\n | editor-last = Hugman\n | title = The PFA Footballers' Who's Who 2010\u201311\n | year = 2010\n | publisher = Mainstream Publishing\n | isbn = 978-1-84596-601-0\n | page = 194 }}</ref>\n| birth_date          = {{birth date and age|1989|12|28|df=y}}<ref name=\"Hugman2010-11\"/>\n| birth_place         = [[Gateshead]], England\n| height              = {{height|ft=6|in=1}}<ref name=\"Profiles\">{{Cite web\n| title = Profiles\n| url = http://origin-www.hartlepoolunited.co.uk/page/ProfilesDetail/0,,10326~41475,00.html\n| publisher = Hartlepool United F.C\n| accessdate = 19 October 2012}}</ref>\n| position            = [[Forward (association football)|Striker]]\n| curr