{"title_page": "Know Better Learn Faster", "text_new": "{{Infobox album\n| name       = Know Better Learn Faster\n| type       = [[Album]]\n| artist     = [[Thao with the Get Down Stay Down]]\n| cover      = Thao Know Better Learn Faster cover.jpg\n| alt        =\n| released   = October 13, 2009\n| recorded   =\n| venue      =\n| studio     =\n| genre      = [[Rock music|Rock]]\n| length     =\n| label      = [[Kill Rock Stars]]\n| producer   = [[Tucker Martine]]\n| prev_title = [[We Brave Bee Stings and All]]\n| prev_year  = 2008\n| next_title = [[We the Common]]\n| next_year  = 2013\n}}\n\n'''''Know Better Learn Faster''''' is a studio [[album]] by [[alternative rock|alternative]] [[folk rock|folk]] band [[Thao with the Get Down Stay Down|Thao & The Get Down Stay Down]]. It was released on October 13, 2009 on the [[Kill Rock Stars]] label.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/know-better-learn-faster-mw0001765559|title=Know Better Learn Faster - Thao & the Get Down Stay Down {{!}} Songs, Reviews, Credits {{!}} AllMusic|website=AllMusic|access-date=2016-04-08}}</ref>\n\n{{Album reviews\n|rev1=[[Paste Magazine]]\n|rev1Score=(8.6/10)[http://www.pastemagazine.com/articles/2009/10/thao-with-the-get-down-stay-down-know-better-learn.html link]\n|rev2=[[Pitchfork Media|Pitchfork]]\n|rev2Score = (7.8/10)[http://pitchfork.com/reviews/albums/13583-know-better-learn-faster/ link] \n|rev3 = \n|rev3Score =  \n}}\n\n== Background ==\n\"The record is primarily a response to the end of a relationship, so a lot of it is pretty reactionary. It\u2019s trying to be introspective, but there\u2019s always got to be a little 'fuck you' in there \u2013 or, sometimes there\u2019s a lot.\"<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.fuelfriendsblog.com/2009/06/03/warding-off-demons-with-thao-nguyen-interview/|title=Warding off demons with Thao Nguyen (Interview) {{!}} Fuel/Friends Music Blog|website=www.fuelfriendsblog.com|access-date=2016-04-13}}</ref>\n\n== Title ==\nThao Nguyen explained the title of the album in an interview with [[KEXP-FM|KEXP]]: \u201cThe album is named \u2018Know Better Learn Faster\u2019 because you can't. By the time you realize you should, it's too late. And I enjoy the predicament and the totally devastating, unfunny humor of that.\u201d<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://blog.kexp.org/2009/09/30/song-of-the-day-thao-with-the-get-down-stay-down-know-better-learn-faster/|title=Song of the Day: Thao with The Get Down Stay Down \u2013 Know Better Learn Faster|last=Cullen|first=Brian|website=The KEXP Blog|access-date=2016-04-13}}</ref>\n\n==Track listing==\n{{Track listing\n| all_writing = \n| title1 = The Clap\n| length1 = 0:33\n| title2 = Cool Yourself\n| length2 = 2:34\n| title3 = When We Swam\n| length3 = 2:58\n| title4 = Know Better Learn Faster\n| length4 = 3:49\n| title5 = Body\n| length5 = 3:12\n| title6 = The Give\n| length6 = 3:43\n| title7 = Good Bye Good Luck\n| length7 = 2:22\n| title8 = Trouble Was For\n| length8 = 2:47\n| title9 = Oh. No.\n| length9 = 2:46\n| title10 = Fixed It!\n| length10 = 2:57\n| title11 = Burn You Up\n| length11 = 2:28\n| title12 = But What of the Strangers\n| length12 = 3:37\n| title13 = Easy\n| length13 = 3:37\n}}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [http://www.thaomusic.com/ Thao Nguyen official website]\n\n[[Category:Thao & The Get Down Stay Down albums]]\n[[Category:2009 albums]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox album\n| name       = Know Better Learn Faster\n| type       = [[Album]]\n| artist     = [[Thao with the Get Down Stay Down]]\n| cover      = Thao Know Better Learn Faster cover.jpg\n| alt        =\n| released   = October 13, 2009\n| recorded   =\n| venue      =\n| studio     =\n| genre      = [[Rock music|Rock]]\n| length     =\n| label      = [[Kill Rock Stars]]\n| producer   = [[Tucker Martine]]\n| prev_title = [[We Brave Bee Stings and All]]\n| prev_year  = 2008\n| next_title = [[We the Common]]\n| next_year  = 2013\n}}\n\n'''''Know Better Learn Faster''''' is a studio [[album]] by [[alternative rock|alternative]] [[folk rock|folk]] band [[Thao with the Get Down Stay Down|Thao & The Get Down Stay Down]]. It was released on October 13, 2009 on the [[Kill Rock Stars]] label.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/know-better-learn-faster-mw0001765559|title=Know Better Learn Faster - Thao & the Get Down Stay Down {{!}} Songs, Reviews, Credits {{!}} AllMusic|website=AllMusic|access-date=2016-04-08}}</ref>\n\n{{Album reviews\n|rev1=[[Paste Magazine]]\n|rev1Score=(8.6/10)[http://www.pastemagazine.com/articles/2009/10/thao-with-the-get-down-stay-down-know-better-learn.html link]\n|rev2=[[Pitchfork Media|Pitchfork]]\n|rev2Score = (7.8/10)[http://pitchfork.com/reviews/albums/13583-know-better-learn-faster/ link] \n|rev3 = \n|rev3Score =  \n}}\n\n== Background ==\n\"The record is primarily a response to the end of a relationship, so a lot of it is pretty reactionary. It\u2019s trying to be introspective, but there\u2019s always got to be a little 'fuck you' in there \u2013 or, sometimes there\u2019s a lot.\"<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.fuelfriendsblog.com/2009/06/03/warding-off-demons-with-thao-nguyen-interview/|title=Warding off demons with Thao Nguyen (Interview) {{!}} Fuel/Friends Music Blog|website=www.fuelfriendsblog.com|access-date=2016-04-13}}</ref>\n\n== Title ==\nThao Nguyen explained the title of the album in an interview with [[KEXP-FM|KEXP]]: \u201cThe album is named \u2018Know Better Learn Faster\u2019 because you can\u2019t. By the time you realize you should, it\u2019s too late. And I enjoy the predicament and the totally devastating, unfunny humor of that.\u201d<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://blog.kexp.org/2009/09/30/song-of-the-day-thao-with-the-get-down-stay-down-know-better-learn-faster/|title=Song of the Day: Thao with The Get Down Stay Down \u2013 Know Better Learn Faster|last=Cullen|first=Brian|website=The KEXP Blog|access-date=2016-04-13}}</ref>\n\n==Track listing==\n{{Track listing\n| all_writing = \n| title1 = 